	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001097_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Burnbank</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Hamilton,</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">14<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> Sept 1857 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Sir </p>
<lb/><p>It certainly 
<lb/>would be very 
<lb/>nice to spend a 
<lb/>short time in 
<lb/>the pleasant 
<lb/>haunts to which 
<lb/>you most kindly 
<lb/>invite me, but 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001097_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>I think that duty 
<lb/>compels me to 
<lb/>decline the enjoy
<lb/>ment. I am at 
<lb/>present lionizing - 
<lb/>a work to which 
<lb/>I have no appetite, 
<lb/>but different 
<lb/>friends seem

<lb/>anxious for it 
<lb/>and I think it 
<lb/>may lead to the 
<lb/>opening of <placeName>Africa</placeName>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001097_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>to the gospel and 
<lb/>submit accordingly<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>If <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Cecil</persName> is 
<lb/>with you, pray 
<lb/>present my 
<lb/>kindest regards<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I have not had 
<lb/>time to call on 
<lb/>him since my 
<lb/>return and indeed 
<lb/>I have gone no 
<lb/>where on pleasure<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I only saw the 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001097_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/><placeName><choice><sic>Chrystal</sic><corr>crystal</corr></choice> Palace</placeName> once 
<lb/>when about to 
<lb/>leave <placeName>London</placeName>
<lb/>and the Art treasure 
<lb/>exhibition when 
<lb/>about to leave 
<lb/><placeName>Manchester</placeName>. <choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>he 
<lb/>book is all in the 
<lb/>printer's hands &amp; 
<lb/>will be published 
<lb/>on 10<hi rend="sup">th</hi> November<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>With many thanks 
<lb/>for your kindness<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I am &amp;c 
<lb/><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
